
Installation
------------
 	 
 sudo apt install php7.2-cli php-mysql   
 sudo apt install apt-transport-https lsb-release ca-certificates


Extenstions
-----------

Extenstion configuration goes to:
 /etc/php/<version>/mods_enabled

To find the configuration file and scanned directories:
 php -i     # extension dir

To find where extesions are placed:
 php -i | grep -i extension.*dir

To list installed modules:
 php -m

Notable configuration directives:
 allow_url_fopen
